snippet.title: Mite wa Ikenai: Ghost Photos You Shouldn't Look At 01
snippet.description:
Join: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9o-HIry3DcOM1P6t_eVNFw/join
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/taraadevlin
Merch: https://teespring.com/stores/kowabana
Discord: https://discord.gg/DzAdr3Q
Sumikowa: The Haunting of Higanbana Heights: https://amzn.to/3csbfuv

Mite wa Ikenai is a DS game that features a bunch of Japanese ghost photos you have to scan for hints of the supernatural!

Website: http://www.kowabana.net/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/taraadevlin/

Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/taraadevlin
